WEBVTT

00:00:00.719 --> 00:00:02.279
Tazama usanifu huu.

00:00:04.178 --> 00:00:05.697
Ni kipi ambacho unaona?

00:00:07.064 --> 00:00:10.715
Kwa mtazamo wa kwanza, inaonekana
kuwa ni saa ya babu

00:00:10.739 --> 00:00:12.482
ikiwa na karatasi lililotupiwa juu

00:00:12.506 --> 00:00:14.402
na kamba iliyozunguka katikati.

00:00:15.657 --> 00:00:18.705
Ila mtazamo wa kwanza mara zote huruhusu
wa pili.

00:00:19.591 --> 00:00:20.741
Angalia tena.

00:00:21.751 --> 00:00:22.901
Unaona nini sasa?

00:00:23.830 --> 00:00:25.743
Ukiangalia kwa karibu zaidi,

00:00:25.767 --> 00:00:29.917
utatambua kwamba usanifu huu mzima

00:00:29.941 --> 00:00:32.469
umetengenezwa na kipande kimoja cha
sanamu.